item.title: Version 2.5.0 Release Notes
item.description: This document outlines the main additions and changes to the Iguazio MLOps Platform ("the platform") in version 2.5.0, and known issues in this version. Tech Preview NoteThe "[Tech Preview]" notation marks features that are included in the current release as a sneak peek to future release features but without official support in this release. Note that Tech Preview features don't go through QA cycles and might result in unexpected behavior.
